CUSTOMER AUTHORIZATION
THIS IS AN ESTIMATE, NOT A CONTRACT FOR SERVICES. The summary above is furnished by Reliable Plumbing Plus as a good
faith estimate of work to be performed at the location described above and is based on our evaluation and does not include

work has started. I understand that the final cost of the work may differ from the estimate, perhaps materially. The company
shall not be liable for any irrigation, trees, shrubs, or any unforeseen items out of our control. THIS IS NOT A GUARANTEE OF
THE FINAL PRICE OF WORK TO BE PERFORMED. I agree and authorize the work as summarized on these estimated terms,
and I agree to pay the full amount for all work performed. A restocking fee of 25% will be applied to all special order and non
truck stock items on cancelations. Any change of work orders are to be conducted as a separate estimate and must be
approved before performing any work. Upon approval of this estimate you the customer agree to sign and deliver a notice of
commencement at our office upon demand. All work performed is strictly C.O.D.
